about.summary: Functions for server CLI applications used by humans.

name: path-and-address
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "path-and-address" %}
{% set version = "2.0.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.zip
  sha256: e96363d982b3a2de8531f4cd5f086b51d0248b58527227d43cf5014d045371b7

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - path_and_address

about:
  home: https://github.com/joeyespo/path-and-address
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Functions for server CLI applications used by humans.'

  dev_url: https://github.com/joeyespo/path-and-address

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - synapticarbors
